'''湯姆·勞倫斯'''（{{lang-en|Tom Lawrence}}；{{bd|1994年|1月13日}}）是一位[[威爾士|威爾士]]足球運動員。在場上的位置是前鋒。他現在效力於[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠]]球隊[[德比郡足球俱乐部|德比郡]]。他出身自曼聯青訓營。他也代表威爾士國青隊參賽<ref>{{cite news |title=Football: Manchester United’s former Flintshire Schools’ FA starlet Tom Lawrence scores first goal for Wales Under 21s in Moldova win |url=http://www.dailypost.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/football-manchester-uniteds-former-flintshire-2637809 |work=Daily Post |publisher=Trinity Mirror |date=28 March 2013 |accessdate=2 December 2013 |archive-date=2015-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150910031500/http://www.dailypost.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/football-manchester-uniteds-former-flintshire-2637809 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

